 г. в местности еркшир, Англия. Его родителей звали Robert Ryther и Lady Margaret Southeby. Он женился на женщине по имени Dame Sibyl Aldeburgh около 1384 г. в местности еркшир, Англия. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын. Он жил в местности харюуд, еркшир, Англия, Великобритания в 1395 году. Он умер около 1426 г. в местности еркшир, Англия в возрасте 78 лет и был похоронен в местности харюуд, еркшир, Англия."},"sm":{"about 1350–about 1426":"e tusa o le 1350–e tusa o le 1426","1350–1426":"1350–1426","1366–1439":"1366–1439","1379–1440":"1379–1440","–1379":"–1379","1335–1363":"1335–1363","1363":"1363","1440":"1440","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1384–1390":"mai le 1384 e o'o I le 1390","1426":"1426","1379":"1379","1335":"1335","about 1426":"e tusa o le 1426","1366":"1366","between 1395 and 1398":"mai le 1395 e o'o I le 1398","vóór 1379":"a'e le'I oo le 1379","about 1350":"e tusa o le 1350","1439":"1439","about 1384":"e tusa o le 1384","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, Egelani","Harewood, West Yorkshire, kingdom of England":"Harewood, Yorkshire, Egelani, United Kingdom","Yorkshire, Kingdom of England":"Yorkshire, Egelani, United Kingdom","Harewood, Yorkshire, England":"Harewood, Yorkshire, Egelani","Ryther, Yorkshire, England":"Ryther, Yorkshire, Egelani"},"sk":{"about 1350–about 1426":"okolo 1350–okolo 1426","1350–1426":"1350–1426","1366–1439":"1366–1439","1379–1440":"1379–1440","–1379":"–1379","1335–1363":"1335–1363","1363":"1363","1440":"1440","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1384–1390":"od 1384 do 1390","1426":"1426","1379":"1379","1335":"1335","about 1426":"okolo 1426","1366":"1366","between 1395 and 1398":"od 1395 do 1398","vóór 1379":"pred rokom 1379","about 1350":"okolo 1350","1439":"1439","about 1384":"okolo 1384","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","Harewood, West Yorkshire, kingdom of England":"Harewood, Yorkshire, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Yorkshire, Kingdom of England":"Yorkshire, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Harewood, Yorkshire, England":"Harewood, York